          <li>your full name</li>
          <li>your current address and the address on your log book (V5C)</li>
          <li>the registration number of the vehicle you’re asking about</li>
          <li>what information you need, for example when the vehicle was first registered or the date you bought it</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="city-body-m">You can send your request to DVLA by email or post.</p>

        <p class="city-body-m"><strong><abbr title="Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency">DVLA</abbr> SAR Enquiries</strong><br><a href="mailto:SubjectAccess.Requests@dvla.gsi.gov.uk" class="city-link">SubjectAccess.Requests@dvla.gsi.gov.uk</a></p>

        <p class="city-body-m">
          SAR Enquiries
          <br>DVRE
